<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5"> صحيح:</span> م <span class="c2">(٨/ ١٣٠)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>